p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
&lt;/style>&lt;/head>&lt;body style=" font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:8.25pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;">
&lt;p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">KY-037 high sensitivity sound detection module is an analog/digital sensor that uses a condenser microphone to observe changes in environment noise.&lt;/p>&lt;/body>&lt;/html></description>
